    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission decision.",
